title: 04/29/22 DPS Hour 2 - Rich Eisen
itunes:title: 04/29/22 DPS Hour 2 - Rich Eisen
description:
In hour 2 the NFL Draft still leads the pack! Though the guys take a deeper look into how draft picks are setting up some teams for trades. The guys also have a little fun with the composure of commissioner Roger Goodell. Rich Eisen also joins to give his perspective on how the 1st round played out and what its like reacting in person, live from Las Vegas.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
